<Author>Mairmi
<Content>Go for it! My husband and I have just returned from Hollywood Media Hotel where we stayed for the past week. The hotel is excellent. Its location is on one of the main shopping streets in Berlin. The atmosphere in the hotel is very relaxed and staff are very friendly and professional. The breakfasts in the hotel are amazing. A huge selection to choose from each morning with a different selection of hot food presented each day. The dining room is run with excellent efficiency and the staff in the breakfast room are eager to please. There is absolutely no shortage of food, either hot or cold!There is also a small gym on the top floor of the hotel which I used everyday and never had to wait as I was the only person in the gym each day! The hollywood theme works very well and it certainly is not 'in your face'. Overall, the location is excellent as there is a bus stop outside the door with a fantastic public transport system. I really recommend this hotel for any tourists in Berlin. 
